3FF43762.Line5.137EC4: No gift can restore what Crane destroyed, but I must know where Ealda found this. Perhaps...I will ask her.

67708DA0.Line3.137EC4: This is Arreat steel...smithed in the forges of Harrogath before the mountain fell...

8EECE3DE.Line1.137EC4: I am sorry, but I cannot accept--

902A632F.VoiceDir5.137EC4: Regaining composure, yet still impressed. Receptive.

B7A6B96D.VoiceDir3.137EC4: Eyes widen, surprised to see the steel. Reverent.

DF230FAB.VoiceDir1.137EC4: Firm. Flat refusal, interrupted by seeing the gift.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “The Crane Tribe sends a gift. Ealda wants to meet.”
